                        Road Signs For Lightwave 3D
                              By Jose Burgos

                        (C) 1994 Merlin's Software
  
    Road Signs is a collection of over 50 Lightwave objects. A must for
    accident reconstruction or any out door scene. It consist of all
    major US traffic signs, including Routes, Interstates, and Highway
    signs. These are all hand crafted not digitized. Includes Road Signs
    Construction Kit which allows you to simply add text to create an
    unlimited number of signs and the ability to tailor the sign to fit
    your scene.
 
    Road Signs requires Lightwave 3.0 or higher and about 1 megabyte
    of Hard drive space. An install program is included that sets it up
    to automatically come up in Lightwave.
  
    Suggested Retail Price: $59.95
  
    Road Signs is distributed by Visual Inspirations in Tampa, FL. You
    can order direct. It's also carried by the major Amiga distributors
    so you should be able to purchase it from your local dealer.
  
    If you tell us you saw this demo pic you can order Road Signs direct
    from Visual Inspirations for only $45.00 and we pay shipping anywhere
    in the US & Canada.  
  
